ane%20Cardinale%20-%20Corbis%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiny%20tattoos%20are%20gaining%20popularity%20as%20a%20form%20of%20smaller%20conspicuous%20consumption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20a%20small%20status%20symbol%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20reflecting%20disposable%20income%20and%20identity%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trend%20aligns%20with%20rising%20consumerism%20and%20changing%20perceptions%20of%20tattoos%20in%20society.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20day%2C%20my%20sister%20and%20I%20found%20ourselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tattoos-helped-me-love-my-body-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewaiting%20for%20tattoos%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20New%20York%20City%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20this%20was%20not%20a%20sketchy%20setup%3B%20instead%2C%20a%20popular%20tattoo%20studio%20was%20offering%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoo-artist-what-not-to-do-when-getting-first-tattoo-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Especial%20flash%20tattoo%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20For%20%2420%20to%20%2440%2C%20you%20could%20pick%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoo-artist-what-to-avoid-when-getting-tiny-tattoo-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealready-sketched%20tiny%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20it%20permanently%20inked%20onto%20your%20body.%20The%20deal%20was%20so%20popular%20that%20we%20waited%20for%20over%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20eventually%20had%20to%20depart%20for%20our%20next%20destination%20tattoo-less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoo-artist-what-to-avoid-when-getting-tiny-tattoo-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiny%20tattoos%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fine-line%20tattoos%20have%20exploded%20in%20popularity.%20These%20designs%20are%20often%20black%2C%20minimal%2C%20delicate%2C%20and%20not%20as%20cost-%20or%20time-intensive%20as%20larger%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20floodgates%20have%20opened%20in%20the%20world%20of%20smaller%20tattoos%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sam%20Kelly%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Tiny%20Zaps%2C%20a%20studio%20in%20New%20York%20City%20that%20offers%20a%20library%20of%20small%20designs%20by%20tattoo%20artists%20across%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20consumer%2C%20it's%20no%20longer%20this%20big%20body%20modification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20pair%20of%20matching%20buddy%20tattoos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ba018957d362d375e78f3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBuddy%26quot%3B%20tiny%20tattoos%20at%20Tiny%20Zaps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tiny%20Zaps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tiny%20tattoo%20has%20become%20a%20status%20symbol%20that%20can%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esignal%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-luxury-needs-to-die-luxury-brand-earnings-bofa-analysts-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eepitome%20of%20small%20luxury%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20They're%20just%20pricey%20enough%20to%20show%20a%20person%20has%20enough%20disposable%20income%20to%20drop%20on%20a%20freckle-sized%20permanent%20alteration.%20(Despite%20the%20big%20New%20York%20City%20flash%20sale%2C%20most%20cost%20around%20at%20minimum%20around%20%2450%20to%20%2470%20and%20often%20tip%20into%20the%20three-figures.)%20And%20they%20telegraph%20%E2%80%94%20quietly%20%E2%80%94%20that%20you're%20young%20or%20in-the-know%20enough%20to%20exhibit%20a%20nihilism%20that%20says%3A%20%3Cem%3EWhy%20not%3C%2Fem%3E%20get%20a%20silly%20doodle%20permanently%20inked%20into%20my%20skin%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnjl%20Nath%2C%2026%2C%20a%20musician%20and%20actor%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20went%20from%20having%20zero%20tattoos%20to%20two%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20I'd%20actually%20get%20one%20until%20I%20learned%20about%20fine%20line%20tattoos%20and%20the%20daintier%20smaller%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Nath%20said.%20The%20rise%20in%20popularity%20of%20small%20tattoos%20influenced%20her%20to%20finally%20bite%20the%20bullet.%20She%20loved%20her%20first%20one%20so%20much%20that%20she%20ended%20up%20getting%20in%20another%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20just%20went%20into%20it%20thinking%20life%20is%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20generation%2C%20people%20just%20have%20that%20mindset%20of%20going%20after%20what%20they%20want%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20really%20cool.%20Of%20course%2C%20tattoos%20are%20such%20a%20permanent%20thing%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20generation%20sees%20maybe%20small%20tattoos%20as%20more%20of%20just%20a%20whimsical%2C%20fun%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22262e7aee-ec0a-404f-98d1-dbefae19cba8%5C%22%3ETattoos%20as%20a%20form%20of%20conspicuous%20consumption%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20the%20tiny%20tattoo%20makes%20sense%20in%20an%20America%20that's%20becoming%20more%20inked%20and%20increasingly%20expressing%20identity%20through%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-stuff-economy-prices-american-dream-housing-televisions-tariffs-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20things%20we%20choose%20to%20consume%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%20Pew%20Research%20survey%20of%208%2C480%20adults%20found%20that%20around%20a%20third%20of%20American%20adults%20have%20a%20tattoo%2C%20and%20younger%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20those%20who%20fall%20loosely%20into%20the%20millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20buckets%20%E2%80%94%20were%20the%20most%20likely%20across%20age%20groups%20to%20have%20a%20tattoo.%20For%20instance%2C%2041%25%20of%20respondents%20under%2030%20said%20they%20had%20at%20least%20one%20tattoo%20vs.%2025%25%20of%20those%20ages%2050%20to%2064.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20to%20gauge%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20tattoo%3A%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20people%20giving%20them.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20number%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.bls.gov%2Fcew%2Fapps%2Ftable_maker%2Fv4%2Ftable_maker.htm%23type%3D17%26amp%3Bfrom%3D2020%26amp%3Bto%3D2024%26amp%3Bqtr%3D1%26amp%3Bown%3D5%26amp%3Bind%3D812199%26amp%3Barea%3DUS000%26amp%3Bsupp%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20personal%20care%20services%26quot%3B%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20tattoo%20parlors%2C%20ear%20piercing%20services%2C%20and%20tanning%20salons%2C%20has%20seen%20employment%20jump%20from%20150%2C000%20at%20the%20start%20of%202020%20to%20a%20little%20over%20180%2C000%20at%20the%20start%20of%202024.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-spending-consumers-economic-sentiment-retail-sales-inflation-gdp-growth-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rise%20in%20consumerism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coupled%20with%20Americans'%20desires%20to%20reward%20themselves%20with%20little%20treats%2C%20might%20mean%20a%20tiny%20tattoo%20falls%20into%20the%20category%20of%20a%20small%2C%20fun%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20I'm%20willing%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20and%20maybe%20not%20spend%20as%20much%20money%20eating%20out%20or%20on%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20Nath%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20feel%20like%20it%20is%20a%20small%20luxury%2C%20definitely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20selfie%20of%20Angl%20Nath%20showing%20her%20tiny%20tattoo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ba0735f9db348adc0adf47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnjl%20Nath%20has%20become%20hooked%20on%20tiny%20tattoos.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Angl%20Nath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.popsugar.com%2Fbeauty%2Fhailey-bieber-tattoos-47282350%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemulate%20celebrity%20it-girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Zo%C3%AB%20Kravitz%2C%20who%20have%20increasingly%20sported%20tiny%20tattoos%20of%20their%20own.%20And%20online%20search%20interest%20in%20%26quot%3Bfine-line%20tattoos%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20common%20type%20of%20tiny%20tattoo%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20surged.%20There%20are%20nearly%20469%2C000%20posts%20with%20%23finelinetattoo%20on%20TikTok%2C%20and%20search%20interest%20in%20the%20term%20has%20spiked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fm4UiU%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fm4UiU%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20kind%20of%20joke%20around%20where%20Tiny%20Zaps%20is%20a%20toy%20store%20or%20a%20candy%20store%20for%20adults.%20It's%20like%20a%20treat%20yourself%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20cofounder%20Kelly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETattoos%20are%20a%20part%20of%20what's%20called%20identity%20signaling%2C%20wherein%20someone%20opts%20for%20a%20visible%20change%2C%20style%20of%20talking%2C%20or%20product%20to%20signal%20something%20about%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20think%20a%20soccer%20mom%20driving%20an%20SUV%20or%20a%20Wall%20Street%20bro%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-status-symbol-men-golf-courseshirt-club-masters-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewearing%20a%20golf%20polo%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20fancy%20course.%20Tattoos%20are%20a%20more%20radical%20form%20of%20identity%20signaling%2C%20since%20they%20are%20permanent%20(or%20painful%20and%20costly%20to%20remove).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20think%20about%20tiny%20tattoos%20as%20a%20form%20of%20conspicuous%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20J.%20Jobu%20Babin%2C%20a%20behavioral%20scientist%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Northern%20Iowa%20who%20studies%20the%20economics%20of%20beauty.%20Conspicuous%20consumption%20is%20when%20one%20buys%20something%20to%20display%20wealth%20and%20social%20status%2C%20and%20Babin%20said%20that%20tiny%20tattoos%20might%20be%20a%20less%20ostentatious%20form%20of%20conspicuous%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20still%20serve%20as%20an%20outward%20marker%20of%20self-expression%2C%20or%20maybe%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20Babin%20said.%20You're%20signaling%20something%20about%20your%20identity%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20your%20tiny%20tattoo%20is%20an%20archaic%20reference%20to%20a%20favorite%20song%20or%20television%20show%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you're%20also%20showing%20that%20you%20have%20the%20time%2C%20disposable%20income%2C%20and%20commitment%20to%20getting%20something%20inked%20onto%20you.%20Some%20artists%20require%20minimums%2C%20often%20around%20%24200%2C%20to%20do%20any%20form%20of%20tattoo%3B%20others%20that%20are%20more%20flash-heavy%20can%20range%20from%20around%20%2450%20to%20%24250.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Clinch%2C%20a%20tattoo%20artist%20who%20specializes%20in%20fine-line%20tattoos%2C%20said%20that%20when%20she%20was%20working%20in%20a%20tattoo%20shop%2C%20they'd%20get%20phone%20calls%20every%20day%20from%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20treat%20themselves%20to%20tattoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221185%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20tiny%20tattoo%20of%20the%20letter%20J%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9f85532af4d666ef7481d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221490%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20tiny%20tattoo%20by%20Taylor%20Clinch.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Taylor%20Clinch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20someone%20thought%20tattoos%2C%20they%20thought%2C%20almost%20just%3A%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20professionalism.%26quot%3B%20Whereas%20now%20tattoos%20are%20classifying%20more%20as%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20Clinch%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20money%20to%20get%20quality%20tattoos%2C%20then%20you%20are%20financially%20stable%20or%20you're%20financially%20thriving.%20And%20it%20is%20almost%20equivalent%20to%20a%20spa%20day%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8527849-f2c0-47f2-8c46-611a67d3db53%5C%22%3EScrew%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0get%20a%20tattoo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20tattoos%20differ%20from%20dyeing%20your%20hair%20on%20a%20whim%20or%20going%20in%20for%20a%20spa%20treatment%3B%20they're%20going%20to%20live%20permanently%20in%20your%20skin.%20And%20they%20also%20carry%20their%20own%20ramifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20research%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1111%2Flabr.12167%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20visible%20tattoos%20are%20associated%20with%20a%20drop%20in%20income.%20But%20the%20research%20also%20said%20that%20as%20the%20number%20of%20people%20getting%20a%20first%20tattoo%20increases%2C%20one%20key%20question%20is%20whether%20%26quot%3Bthe%20correlation%20between%20tattoos%20and%20less%20favorable%20socioeconomic%20characteristics%20will%20dissipate%20over%20time%20%E2%80%94%20and%20with%20it%2C%20the%20still%20primarily%20negative%20stereotypes%20that%20are%20associated%20with%20tattoos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETiny%20designs%20might%20elide%20some%20of%20that%20tattoo%20stigma%2C%20which%20some%20Americans%20say%20is%20already%20dissipating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Lane%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Illinois%20State%20University%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Other%20End%20of%20the%20Needle%3A%20Continuity%20and%20Change%20among%20Tattoo%20Workers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20it's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20show%20your%20mom%20a%20tiny%20tattoo%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20than%20a%20larger%20or%20more%20intense%20design.%20In%20research%20Lane%20presented%20recently%20on%20tattooing%20and%20stigma%2C%20people%20with%20tattoos%20singled%20out%20their%20mothers%20as%20the%20people%20who%20most%20often%20judged%20them%20for%20their%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20might%20be%20changing.%20Kelly%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Tiny%20Zaps%2C%20has%20seen%20plenty%20of%20mother-daughter%20pairs%20come%20into%20the%20store.%20He%20also%20said%20he's%20seen%20some%20of%20the%20more%20generational%20stigma%20disintegrating%20before%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20some%20popups%20at%20hotels%20and%20we've%20legitimately%20had%20groups%20of%2075-year-old%20grandmas%20on%20trips%20together%20all%20getting%20their%20first%20tattoos%2C%20sipping%20white%20wine%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENath%2C%20the%20tiny%20tattooed%20Gen%20Zer%2C%20keeps%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20refrain%20that%20life%20is%20short.%20She%20feels%20like%20getting%20tattoos%20has%20helped%20empower%20her%20to%20live%20in%20the%20moment%20and%20not%20overthink%20her%20decision-making.%20But%20there%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20another%20advantage%20of%20the%20tiny%20tattoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20technology%20of%20tattoo%20laser%20removal%3B%20I'm%20like%2C%20if%20I%20really%20regret%20this%20when%20I'm%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%20years%20old%2C%20I%20could%20technically%20get%20it%20taken%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Nath%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20that%20aspect%20of%20like%2C%20it%20is%20permanent%2C%20but%20is%20it%20really%20now%20with%20technology%3F%20If%20I%20really%20don't%20want%20this%20on%20me%2C%20I%20could%20get%20it%20removed%20one%20day.%20That%20helps%20relieve%20the%20pressure%20of%20making%20that%20type%20of%20decision.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-tattoo-fine-line-tattoos-trend-luxury-status-symbol-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757144281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb39fdf9db348adc0af531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-tattoo-fine-line-tattoos-trend-luxury-status-symbol-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Are%20you%20seeing%20tiny%20tattoos%20everywhere%20you%20look%3F%20They're%20a%20beloved%20status%20symbol.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jkaplan%40businessinsider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-tattoo-fine-line-tattoos-trend-luxury-status-symbol-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98God%E2%80%99s%20influencer%E2%80%99%3A%20Italian%20teenager%20who%20died%20at%2015%20to%20become%20the%20first%20millennial%20saint%3B%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%98saint-next-door%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757144099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123732198%2Cimgsize-888879.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgods-influencer-italian-teenager-who-died-at-15-to-become-the-first-millennial-saint-considered-a-saint-next-door%2Farticleshow%2F123732196.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F123732196.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECarlo%20Acutis%2C%20an%20Italian%20teenager%20celebrated%20for%20his%20computer%20skills%20and%20devotion%20to%20Catholicism%2C%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20Catholic%20Church's%20first%20millennial%20saint.%20Known%20as%20%26quot%3BGod's%20influencer%2C%26quot%3B%20Acutis%2C%20who%20died%20in%202006%2C%20will%