20for%20all%20iOS%20users%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20users%20were%20able%20to%20get%20off%20the%20waitlist%20but%20were%20put%20right%20back%20on%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20just%20one%20example%20of%20how%20the%20service%20is%20in%20its%20early%20stages%20as%20it%20quickly%20moves%20to%20expand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after%20a%20few%20months%20of%20waiting%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20flying%20out%20to%20Austin%20just%20to%20ride%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-officially-launches-robotaxi-pilot-austin-flat-fee-elon-musk-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%20Robotaxi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20scored%20a%20golden%20ticket%20for%20the%20service%20late%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20lost%20it%20a%20day%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20time%20in%20the%20quasi-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-access-invite-exclusive-club-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20club%20of%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%3C%2Fa%3E%20testers%20was%20short-lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Tesla%20made%20the%20Robotaxi%20app%20available%20to%20all%20iOS%20users%2C%20allowing%20the%20public%20to%20join%20a%20waitlist%20for%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20downloaded%20the%20app%20and%20joined%20the%20waitlist%20around%208%3A30%20p.m.%20PT%20on%20Wednesday.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20I%20was%20taken%20off%20the%20waitlist%20in%20about%20three%20hours.%20Users%20on%20X%20reported%20a%20similar%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20because%20the%20public%20rollout%20of%20the%20app%20didn't%20come%20with%20an%20announcement%20from%20Tesla%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Robotaxi%20would%20add%20more%20cars%20to%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20or%20Austin%2C%20where%20the%20service%20currently%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20cars%20mean%20a%20better%20ability%20to%20meet%20the%20demand.%20A%20Tesla%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20users%20like%20me%20were%20taken%20off%20the%20waitlist%20that%20fast%2C%20without%20clarity%20on%20whether%20more%20cars%20were%20put%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20what%20would%20this%20do%20to%20pick-up%20times%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20brief%20time%20with%20the%20app%2C%20the%20pick-up%20ETAs%20were%20high.%20Estimated%20times%20ranged%20from%2012%20minutes%20to%20up%20to%2040%20minutes.%20Twelve%20minutes%20can%20be%20par%20for%20the%20course%20in%20SF%20for%20Uber%20or%20Waymo's%20robotaxis%3B%20but%2040%20minutes%3F%20It%20doesn't%20even%20take%20that%20long%20to%20travel%20across%20a%20congested%20SF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20on%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20I%20noticed%20my%20access%20was%20revoked.%20For%20reasons%20unclear%2C%20I%20had%20to%20sign%20up%20again%20to%20be%20put%20back%20on%20the%20waitlist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20of%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bba78ff9db348adc0afd2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20Robotaxi%20app%20on%20Wednesday%20(left)%20showed%20access%20was%20available.%20By%20Thursday%2C%20I%20was%20put%20back%20on%20the%20waitlist.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20on%20X%20reported%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20access%20to%20%40robotaxi%20all%20day%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20I'm%20back%20on%20the%20waitlist%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BTried%20reinstalling%20the%20app%20too.%20Bug%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2bd62c8-96ba-4620-bc46-a13d660eed48%5C%22%3EEarly%20days%20for%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20not%20to%20air%20out%20frustrations%20about%20getting%20booted.%20(Although%2C%20it'd%20sure%20be%20nice%20to%20get%20it%20back!)%20My%20experience%20and%20that%20of%20others%20are%20a%20reminder%20that%20it's%20still%20early%20days%20for%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20Austin%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20of%20my%20Austin%20trip%2C%20Tesla%20had%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-new-robotaxi-geofence-austin-shape-elon-musk-bigger-waymo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpanded%20the%20geo-fence%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pilot%20launch.%20Tesla's%20VP%20of%20AI%20software%2C%20Ashok%20Elluswamy%2C%20said%20at%20the%20end%20of%20July%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethere%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Bhandful%26quot%3B%20of%20Tesla%20Robotaxis%20on%20the%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobotaxis%20on%20the%20road%20are%20still%20working%20out%20some%20kinks.%20As%20I%20reported%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-robotaxi-autonomous-self-driving-test-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRobotaxi%20vs.%20Waymo%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20story%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20error%20that%20required%20the%20safety%20monitor%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat%20to%20pause%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20early-access%20users%20have%20also%20noted%20interventions%2C%20while%20others%20have%20reported%20incident-free%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPick-up%20times%20during%20my%20trip%20to%20Austin%20also%20weren't%20always%20consistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20second%20geo-fence%20expansion%2C%20Tesla%20said%20on%20August%2026%20that%20the%20service%20area%20now%20stands%20at%20173%20square%20miles.%20The%20company%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20%23%20of%20cars%20available%20by%2050%25%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20city%20but%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20specific%20count.%20So%20a%20handful%20and%20a%20half%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20Waymo%20covers%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-tesla-robotaxi-service-area-expansion-austin-texas-phallic-shaped-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E90%20square%20miles%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20about%20100%20robotaxis%20in%20Austin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Tesla%20also%20started%20taking%20riders%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteslas-ride-hailing-service-live-in-san-francisco-musk-says-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBay%20Area%20on%20July%2031%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20service%20area%20included%20all%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20San%20Jose%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20East%20Bay%20Area%2C%20including%20Berkeley.%20But%20can%20we%20call%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Brobotaxi%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20California%20regulations%2C%20Tesla%20put%20a%20safety%20monitor%20directly%20behind%20the%20wheel.%20In%20Austin%2C%20a%20safety%20monitor%20sits%20in%20the%20front%20passenger%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Texas%2C%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20started%20to%20take%20riders%20on%20the%20highway%20this%20month%20%E2%80%94%20a%20notable%20milestone%20considering%20Waymo%20isn't%20taking%20public%20riders%20on%20the%20highways%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20in-car%20safety%20monitor%20moves%20to%20the%20driver's%20seat%20for%20highway%20rides.%20Tesla%20said%20on%20X%20that%20it%20was%20doing%20so%20out%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20and%20other%20reasons%2C%20some%20critics%20say%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20isn't%20quite%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20(rather%20obviously)%20not%20a%20robotaxi%20if%20there's%20an%20employee%20inside%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-waymo-ceo-john-krafcik-tesla-robotaxi-san-francisco-uber-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJohn%20Krafcik%2C%20the%20ex-Waymo%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20in%20August.