%20terms%20for%20how%20LLMs%20train%20on%20creative%20work.%3Cp%3ERICCARDO%20MILANI%2FHans%20Lucas%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20agreed%20to%20pay%20over%20%241.5%20billion%20to%20authors%20for%20books%20used%20for%20LLM%20training.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20comes%20out%20to%20about%20%243%2C000%20per%20book%2C%20according%20to%20the%20proposed%20settlement%20terms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELawyers%20identified%20about%20500%2C000%20copyrighted%20books.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20agreed%20to%20pay%20over%20%241.5%20billion%20to%20settle%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20authors%20who%20allege%20the%20company%20illegally%20used%20their%20books%20to%20train%20its%20artificial%20intelligence%20models%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Friday%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20class-action%20settlement%2C%20if%20approved%20by%20a%20federal%20judge%2C%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20largest%20publicly%20reported%20copyright%20recovery%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20lawyers%20from%20Anthropic%20and%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20sets%20a%20new%20standard%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-future-copyright-lawsuits-new-york-times-times-authors-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20companies%20compensating%20artists%2C%20authors%2C%20and%20other%20copyright%20holders%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20training%20large%20language%20models%20on%20their%20work%2C%20according%20to%20Justin%20Nelson%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Susman%20Godfrey%20representing%20the%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20landmark%20settlement%20far%20surpasses%20any%20other%20known%20copyright%20recovery%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%20It%20will%20provide%20meaningful%20compensation%20for%20each%20class%20work%20and%20sets%20a%20precedent%20requiring%20AI%20companies%20to%20pay%20copyright%20owners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20proposed%20settlement%2C%20authors%20would%20receive%20an%20estimated%20%243%2C000%20for%20each%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cut-pirated-millions-used-books-train-claude-copyright-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epirated%20book%20used%20to%20train%20Anthropic's%20large%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20power%20its%20popular%20chatbot%2C%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20would%20go%20to%20authors%20whose%20books%20were%20included%20in%20Pirate%20Mirror%20Library%20and%20Library%20Genesis%2C%20two%20databases%20of%20pirated%20books%20Anthropic%20used%20for%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Anthropic%20and%20the%20authors%20believe%20500%2C000%20books%20are%20in%20the%20database%2C%20but%20said%20Anthropic%20would%20shell%20out%20more%20cash%20if%20more%20books%20were%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20settlement%20terms%2C%20Anthropic%20could%20still%20be%20held%20liable%20if%20it%20uses%20pirated%20books%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20AI%20company%20is%20also%20required%20to%20destroy%20its%20copies%20of%20the%20Pirate%20Mirror%20Library%20and%20Library%20Genesis%20datasets%20after%20it%20finishes%20identifying%20and%20paying%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20agreement%20will%20only%20go%20into%20effect%20if%20it%20is%20approved%20by%20US%20District%20Judge%20William%20Alsup%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20case.%20Alsup%20scheduled%20a%20hearing%20for%20Monday%20afternoon%20in%20his%20San%20Francisco%20courtroom%20to%20discuss%20whether%20the%20terms%20are%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20does%20not%20change%20Alsup's%20earlier%20ruling%20that%20Anthropic's%20use%20of%20the%20books%20to%20train%20its%20models%20was%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%26quot%3B%20under%20copyright%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20June%2C%20the%20District%20Court%20issued%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20on%20AI%20development%20and%20copyright%20law%2C%20finding%20that%20Anthropic's%20approach%20to%20training%20AI%20models%20constitutes%20fair%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Aparna%20Sridhar%2C%20Anthropic's%20deputy%20general%20counsel%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BToday's%20settlement%2C%20if%20approved%2C%20will%20resolve%20the%20plaintiffs'%20remaining%20legacy%20claims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlsup's%20summary%20judgment%20ruling%20found%20that%20Anthropic%20had%20used%20over%207%20million%20pirated%20books%20to%20train%20its%20large%20language%20models%2C%20and%20physically%20cut%20up%20and%20scanned%20millions%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20Friday's%20settlement%20terms%2C%20attorneys%20for%20the%20authors%20found%20duplicates%20in%20Anthropic's%20training%20database%20and%2C%20after%20matching%20books%20with%20Copyright%20Office%20registrations%2C%20whittled%20the%20list%20of%20stolen%20books%20down%20to%20465%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20approved%2C%20the%20settlement%20would%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20one%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20and%20most%20sophisticated%20copyright%20lawsuits%20against%20artificial%20intelligence%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20mean%20the%20case%20will%20not%20make%20its%20way%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20could%20have%20taken%20the%20opportunity%20to%20resolve%20lingering%20questions%20about%20copyright%20law%20related%20to%20model%20training%20and%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Friday's%20proposed%20settlement%20terms%2C%20lawyers%20representing%20the%20author%20are%20asking%20Alsup%20to%20approve%2025%25%20of%20the%20over-%241.5%20billion%20settlement%20fund%20to%20go%20to%20their%20legal%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-pay-1-5-billion-authors-books-copyright-settlement-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C