nk%5C%22%3Ecompensation%20plan%20for%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20unveiled%20Friday%20and%20is%20worth%20about%20%241%20trillion%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20keep%20his%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20and%20attention%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20EV%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20super%20ambitious%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20motivates%20Elon%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20outlined%20the%20pay%20package%20on%20Friday%20in%20an%20SEC%20filing.%20The%20filing%20said%20Musk%20would%20earn%20the%20fortune%20if%20he%20completed%20certain%20milestones%20for%20the%20company%2C%20including%20bringing%20Tesla%20to%20at%20least%20%248.5%20trillion%20market%20cap%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenholm%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20proposed%20payout%20may%20seem%20exorbitant%20but%20referred%20to%20the%20multibillion-dollar%20deal%20Tesla's%20board%20approved%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20our%20perspective%2C%20it's%20about%20shooting%20for%20the%20moon%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20ambition%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vision%20%E2%80%94%20that%20we've%20put%20out%20with%20the%20master%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Denholm%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20in%202008%2C%20Musk%20has%20taken%20on%20several%20other%20major%20projects%20and%20a%20few%20side%20quests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20founded%20Neuralink%20in%202016%20and%20The%20Boring%20Company%20in%202017.%20In%202022%2C%20Musk%20acquired%20Twitter%20and%20renamed%20it%20X.%20One%20year%20later%2C%20he%20launched%20xAI.%20He%20is%20also%20still%20the%20CEO%20of%20SpaceX%2C%20which%20he%20founded%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20lot%20of%20jobs%20to%20juggle%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20January%2C%20Musk%20became%20the%20face%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-department-government-efficiency-creation-elon-musk-executive-order-2025-1%5C%