%20take%2C%20ChatGPT%20actually%20had%20the%20middle%20levels%20of%20optimism%20about%20Musk's%20chances%20among%20the%20three%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20gave%2020%25%20and%2025%25%20odds%20that%20Tesla%20would%20meet%20the%20vehicle%20delivery%20and%20FSD%20subscriber%20goals.%20It%20was%20most%20confident%20in%20the%20robotaxi%20milestone%2C%20at%2040%25%20odds%2C%20and%20gave%20the%20bot%20milestone%20a%2030%25%20likelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20EBITDA%20and%20market%20cap%2C%20ChatGPT%20was%20less%20confident%20in%20Musk.%20It%20gave%20Tesla%2010%25%20odds%20of%20reaching%20%24400%20billion%20EBITDA%2C%20and%205%25%20odds%20of%20reaching%20an%20%248.5%20trillion%20market%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20ChatGPT%20estimated%20that%20there%20was%20a%202%25%20chance%20that%20Musk%20would%20hit%20every%20target%2C%20a%20percentage%20it%20stuck%20with%20after%20reviewing%20the%20entire%20SEC%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229eb10957-3c88-4b7b-a46d-b2a41d236349%5C%22%3EGemini%20said%20Musk%20doesn't%20stand%20a%20chance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chat%20with%20Gemini%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb165ff9db348adc0aee31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221010%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGemini%20said%20that%20the%20odds%20Tesla%20hit%20all%20goals%20was%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20zero.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20three%20chatbots%2C%20Google's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%3C%2Fa%3E%20thought%20Musk%20was%20the%20most%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20each%20AI%20was%20given%20the%20same%20prompt%2C%20Gemini%20framed%20its%20answers%20about%20Musk's%20likelihoods%20in%20%26quot%3Bless%20thans.%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20a%20less%20than%2010%25%20chance%