ibuting%20to%20your%20longevity%2C%20Ultrahuman%20will%20keep%20you%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20everything%20we%20just%20mentioned%20sounds%20like%20gibberish%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20ring%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ultrahuman%20does%20use%20sound%20science%20to%20apply%20its%20metrics%20to%20your%20health%2C%20it%20also%20assumes%20you%20already%20understand%20most%20of%20the%20science.%20Out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20it's%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3Bphase%20advance%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blight%20exposure%20timing%26quot%3B%20without%20explaining%20why%20you%20should%20care.%20I've%20been%20a%20health%20science%20writer%20for%20over%2010%20years%2C%20and%20I%20even%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20discerning%20what%20some%20of%20it%20meant%20without%20really%20sitting%20down%20and%20sifting%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20little%20layperson%20context%2C%20so%20unless%20you%20already%20know%20how%20circadian%20biology%20works%2C%20you%20may%20find%20yourself%20Googling%20terms%20just%20to%20understand%20your%20daily%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20hold%20your%20hand%20on%20taking%20charge%20of%20your%20health.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20under%20the%20weather%2C%20there's%20no%20ability%20to%20put%20the%20ring%20into%20%26quot%3Brest%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Brecovery%26quot%3B%20mode%20like%20other%20wearables%20let%20you%20do%2C%20so%20Ultrahuman%20is%20still%20encouraging%20activity%20when%20you%20should%20be%20on%20the%20couch.%20This%20can%20be%20hard%20for%20people%20who%20don't%20slow%20down%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22366926b0-97f1-48c3-8f7b-73a6b2018486%5C%22%3EThe%20brain%20health%20focus%20is%20unique%20and%20intriguing.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20standout%20metric%20of%20the%20Ultrahuman%20Ring%20Air%20is%20whether%20your%20brain's%20glymphatic%20system%20(a%20kind%20of%20nightly%20waste-clearance%20process)%20has%20done%20its%20job%2C%20which%20can%20be%20influenced%20by%20sleep%20quality%20and%20timing.%20This%20metric%20is%20not%20something%20you'll%20find%20on%20any%20other%20mainstream%20wearable%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20interesting%20addition%20for%20anyone%20curious%20about%20neurohealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20view%20of%20sleep%20tracking%20app%20screens%3B%20the%20left%20screen%20shows%20a%20brain%20waste%20clearance%20score%20of%2088%20with%20contributors%20including%201%20hour%2020%20minutes%20of%20deep%20sleep%2C%208%20hours%2025%20minutes%20of%20total%20sleep%2C%20and%20high%20HRV%3B%20the%20right%20screen%20shows%20a%20circadian%20phase%20alignment%20dial%20highlighting%20the%20circadian%20dead%20zone%20with%20a%20countdown%20of%207%20hours%20and%207%20minutes%20remaining.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb23faf9db348adc0af13c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltrahuman%20offers%20unique%20insights%20I%20haven't%20found%20in%20other%20smart%20rings%2C%20like%20info%20about%20brain%20waste%20clearance%20and%20circadian%20phase%20alignment.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20little%20cruel.%20When%20I%20woke%20up%20and%20learned%20my%20brain%20waste%20was%20only%2060%2F100%2C%20I%20panicked%20a%20little%20and%20wondered%20what%20damage%20that%20was%20doing%20to%20my%20day.%20There%20isn't%20a%20lot%20of%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20it%20other%20than%20getting%20better%20sleep%20tonight%20(which%20is%20fair%20but%20not%20terribly%20helpful).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227eea1fbf-7ae1-456d-986a-9416c7ae9067%5C%22%3EThe%20app%20interface%20is%20polished%20%E2%80%94%20but%20could%20be%20clearer.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20smart%20rings%2C%20the%20app%20interface%20is%2090%25%20of%20the%20experience%20since%20it's%20where%20you're%20interpreting%20all%20your%20data.%20I%20found%20the%20Ultrahuman%20app%20to%20be%20polished%20and%20very%20on%20brand%20for%20the%20biohacker%20community%2C%20with%20a%20dark%20background%20and%20minimalist%20icons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20easy%20on%20the%20eyes%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20it%20also%20feels%20crowded%20with%20information.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20text%20and%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20visual%20guidance%20on%20what%20is%20most%20important%20versus%20supplementary%20info.%20Ultrahuman%20uses%20a%20minimal%20color%20scheme%2C%20but%20the%20color%20coding%20isn't%20very%20sensible%20%E2%80%94%20sleep%20and%20recovery%20metrics%20are%20both%20orange-yellow%2C%20but%20then%20sleep%20debt%20is%20green%2C%20the%20same%20as%20movement.%20Why%20isn't%20all%20the%20sleep%20data%20one%20color%2C%20movement%20another%2C%20and%20recovery%20another%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20scrolls%20and%20scrolls%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20understand%20which%20information%20is%20the%20most%20important.%20Ultrahuman%20just%20released%20a%20%26quot%3Bsnapshot%26quot%3B%20feature%20in%20its%20latest%20update%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20at-a-glance%20data%20points%20like%20resting%20heart%20rate%2C%20steps%2C%20and%20active%20hours.%20This%20feature%20is%20indeed%20helpful%20(and%20customizable).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20still%20crowds%20the%20interface%20with%20data%20I%20don't%20fully%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%2C%20like%20my%20sleep%20debt%20(does%20knowing%20I'm%20-0h%203m%20behind%20on%20my%20optimal%20sleep%20really%20need%20to%20be%20front%20and%20center%20among%20important%20data%20points%3F)%20and%20a%20countdown%20to%20when%20my%20circadian%20rhythm%20ends%2C%20with%20no%20clear%20explanation%20of%20what%20action%20I'm%20to%20take%20with%20his%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20unclear%3A%20After%20about%20a%20month%20of%20messing%20around%20in%20the%20app%2C%20I%20realized%20there's%20a%20section%20called%20the%20PowerPlugs%20store%20with%20widgets%20you%20can%20add%20%E2%80%94%20many%20for%20free.%20Some%20are%20already%20pre-loaded%20onto%20my%20interface%2C%20like%20the%20Caffeine%20Window%2C%20but%20others%20I%20could%20add%20and%20felt%20would%20be%20genuinely%20helpful%3A%20a%20Vitamin%20D%20optimizer%20that%20tells%20you%20when%20and%20for%20how%20long%20to%20go%20out%20(helpful%20in%20the%20Northeast%20or%20PNW%20in%20winter)%2C%20a%20social%20jetlag%20tracker%20to%20help%20you%20align%20your%20weekday%20and%20weekend%20schedules%2C%20and%20a%20smart%20alarm%20to%20give%20you%20a%20personalized%20wake-up%20time%20based%20on%20your%20sleep%20goals.%20These%20add-ons%20help%20maximize%20the%20value%20Ultrahuman%20aims%20to%20provide.%20I%20just%20don't%20know%20why%20customizing%20this%20section%20isn't%20part%20of%20the%20app%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22039a64a3-043d-4d8c-8095-f22ed6a939a5%5C%22%3ESome%20of%20the%20health%20improvement%20advice%20is%20pretty%20helpful.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20Ultrahuman%20does%20right%20is%20provide%20actionable%20tips%20on%20how%20you%20can%20improve%20your%20numbers%2C%20namely%20around%20sleep.%20When%20you%20click%20into%2C%20say%2C%20your%20sleep%20index%2C%20Ultrahuman%20provides%20tip%20cards%20that%20have%20an%20illustration%20and%20two%20to%20three%20sentences%20of%20advice%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20and%20advice%20to%20improve%20your%20pre-bedtime%20routine%2C%20sleep%20environment%2C%20and%20things%20like%20avoiding%20food%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20sleep.%20Under%20the%20stats%20for%20your%20heart%20rate%20drop%2C%20Ultrahuman%20has%20tip%20cards%20with%20advice%20on%20ideal%20meal%20timing%2C%20fostering%20a%20calm%20sleep%20environment%2C%20and%20avoiding%20late-night%20stimulants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20visual%20and%20concise%20advice%20in%20the%20tip%20sections%20to%20be%20very%20digestible%20and%20the%20information%20itself%20quite%20helpful.%20While%20it's%20all%20generic%20advice%20of%20what%20might%20help%20you%20improve%20your%20numbers%2C%20it%20goes%20beyond%20the%20basics%20of%20%26quot%3Bavoid%20caffeine%20late%20in%20the%20day%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bturn%20off%20the%20TV%20and%20screens%20an%20hour%20before%20bed%26quot%3B%20and%20gets%20into%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20what%20lesser-known%20stimulants%20might%20be%20keeping%20you%20up%20(late%20exercise%2C%20late%20meals)%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20people%20who%20are%20already%20covering%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fad7929-9ccb-496d-b07a-f07a8840d184%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Where%20it%20falls%20short%5C%22%3EWhere%20it%20falls%20short%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d0fff0b-f134-4a21-ae76-02b37f7c7a50%5C%22%3EBattery%20life%20is%20a%20real%20weak%20point.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBattery%20life%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20features%20of%20a%20wearable%20because%20the%20more%20often%20you%20have%20to%20charge%20it%2C%20the%20more%20dead%20periods%20you%20have%20in%20data%20recording%20(especially%20if%20you%20forget%20to%20put%20it%20back%20on%20right%20away).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20smart%20rings%20I've%20tested%20last%20seven%20to%20eight%20days%20per%20charge%3B%20Ultrahuman%20barely%20makes%20it%20five.%20I'd%20charge%20it%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20and%20find%20it%20at%2030%25%20by%20Friday.%20And%20that's%20in%20battery%20saving%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290e44f47-0028-41e2-aa2a-9f637c287584%5C%22%3EThe%20data%20tracking%20is%20spotty.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20know%20how%20accurate%20your%20biometrics%20are%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20you're%20wearing%20three%20wearables%20at%20once%2C%20like%20I%20was%20during%20testing.%20And%20because%20of%20this%2C%20I%20can%20say%20with%20confidence%3A%20Ultrahuman's%20tracking%20is%20a%20bit%20spotty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20activity%20auto-detection%20is%20unreliable%20%E2%80%94%20it%20regularly%20missed%20lighter%20movement%20entirely%20(like%20a%20dog%20walk)%20and%20regularly%20undercounted%20my%20steps%20by%20roughly%201%2C000%20compared%20to%20what%20my%20Oura%20Ring%20and%20Garmin%20were%20showing%20for%20the%20day.%20And%20unlike%20Oura%20or%20Garmin%2C%20there's%20no%20smart%20learning%20over%20time%20to%20better%20identify%20what%20activity%20you're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sleep%20tracking%20wasn't%20terribly%20sensitive%20either.%20One%20night%2C%20I%20woke%20twice%20%E2%80%94%20once%20from%20a%20nightmare%20where%20I%20had%20trouble%20falling%20back%20asleep%20and%20again%20to%20shut%20a%20door%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20the%20ring%20recorded%20uninterrupted%20sleep.%20For%20a%20device%20that%20calculates%20things%20like%20your%20%26quot%3Bbiological%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20blatant%20level%20of%20inaccuracy%20is%20hard%20to%20ignore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20often%20my%20sleep%20quality%20and%20readiness%20score%20were%20on%20par%20with%20what%20my%20other%20wearables%20reported.%20But%20if%20you%20want%20to%20wear%20a%20smart%20ring%20to%20know%20precisely%20how%20many%20steps%20you're%20getting%20in%20a%20day%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20trust%20the%20Ultrahuman%20Ring%20Air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271a71f3f-6f12-4a71-9268-8dfaeeac4e1f%5C%22%3EIt's%20upping%20its%20women's%20health%20game%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it'll%20cost%20you.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20every%20wearable%20now%20has%20some%20kind%20of%20women's%20health%20component%2C%20from%20simply%20letting%20you%20track%20your%20period%20in%20the%20interface%20to%20acting%20as%20an%20unofficial%20basal%20body%20thermometer%20to%20predict%20your%20ovulation%20and%20fertile%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltrahuman%20has%20long%20offered%20the%20basics%2C%20but%20in%20August%202025%2C%20it%20launched%20more%20advanced%20tracking%3A%20Cycle%20%26amp%3B%20Ovulation%20Pro%20uses%20the%20technology%20of%20a%20proprietary%20algorithm%20called%20OvuSense%20that%20purports%20to%20track%20your%20cycle%20with%2090%25%20accuracy%2C%20predict%20ovulation%20even%20among%20irregular%20cycles%2C%20and%20flag%20hidden%20patterns%2C%20like%20a%20sho