3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-aileen-cannon-just-handed-donald-trump-another-legal-win-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJudge%20Aileen%20Cannon%20%3C%2Fa%3Edismissed%20the%20lawsuit%20just%20two%20days%20after%20Newsmax%20filed%20it%20against%20the%20cable%20news%20giant%20and%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20Fox%20Corp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsmax%20alleged%20in%20its%2031-page%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20Murdoch%20family-controlled%20conglomerate%20held%20an%20illegal%20monopoly%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bright-leaning%20pay%20TV%20news%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20ruled%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsmax-accuses-rival-fox-news-of-holding-an-illegal-monopoly-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENewsmax's%20five-count%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20alleged%20violations%20of%20federal%20and%20state%20antitrust%20laws%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bimpermissible%20'shotgun%20pleading'%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20the%20second%20through%20fifth%20counts%20%26quot%3Bincorporate%20all%20preceding%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump-appointed%20judge%20said%20in%20her%20order%20that%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20%26quot%3Bshotgun%26quot%3B%20complaint%20is%2C%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20complaint%20containing%20multiple%20counts%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20each%20count%20adopts%20the%20allegations%20of%20all%20preceding%20counts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Court%20has%20an%20independent%20obligation%20to%20dismiss%20such%20pleadings%20and%20require%20repleader%2C%26quot%3B%20Cannon%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20the%20legal%20battle%20between%20Newsmax%20and%20Fox%20News%20is%20over.%20Cannon%20gave%20Newsmax%20the%20option%20to%20re-file%20an%20amended%20complaint%20%26quot%3Bthat%20is%20consistent%26quot%3B%20with%20her%20order%20by%20next%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amended%20complaint%20must%20not%20contain%20any%20successive%20counts%20that%20incorporate%20all%20prior%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20Cannon%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Newsmax%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20this%20is%20just%20a%20technical%20matter%20and%20our%20law%20firm%20is%20refiling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fox%20News%20spokesperson%20pointed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20media%20powerhouse%20issued%20Wednesday%20in%20response%20to%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNewsmax%20cannot%20sue%20their%20way%20out%20of%20their%20own%20competitive%20failures%20in%20the%20marketplace%20to%20chase%20headlines%20simply%20because%20they%20can't%20attract%20viewers%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20lawsuit%2C%20Newsmax%20accused%20Fox%20Corp.%20and%20Fox%20News%20of%20engaging%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bexclusionary%20scheme%20to%20increase%20and%20maintain%20its%20dominance%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20right-wing%20cable%20news%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewsmax%20alleged%20that%20if%20not%20for%20Fox's%20%26quot%3Banticompetitive%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20would%20have%20%26quot%3Bachieved%20greater%20pay%20TV%20distribution%26quot%3B%20and%20grown%20into%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%26quot%3B%20media%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleged%20that%20Fox%20pressures%20distributors%20into%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20deals%20that%20block%20those%20distributors%20from%20carrying%20competitors%20of%20Fox%20News%2C%20including%20Newsmax%2C%20or%20imposes%20financial%20penalties%20on%20distributors%20if%20they%20carry%20Newsmax%20or%20other%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewsmax-stock-price-soars-650-ipo-debut-trump-news-frenzy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENewsmax%20went%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20a%20market%20capitalization%20of%20%241.7