re%20kind%20of%20an%20IoT-connected%20place.%20Managing%20all%20this%20without%20failures%20was%20a%20real%20challenge%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A495984%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20challenge%20ended%20when%20he%20discovered%20the%20Kerala-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418409%2Findia-solar-power-electricity-bill-savings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%20startup%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98Energy24by7%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20home%20that%20no%20longer%20fears%20outages%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Suresh%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20iCUBE%202000%20inverter%2C%20paired%20with%20two%20iSTORE%20160Ah%20batteries%20and%20two%20545W%20solar%20panels%20on%20his%20rooftop.%20The%20system%20takes%20care%20of%20his%20daily%20load%20%E2%80%94%20lights%2C%20fans%2C%20pumps%2C%20motors%2C%20shutters%2C%20and%20routers%20%E2%80%94%20while%20cutting%20his%20Kerala%20State%20Electricity%20Board%20(KSEB)%20bills%20by%2045%20to%2065%20units%20a%20month.%20It%20runs%20mainly%20on%20solar%20during%20the%20day%2C%20drawing%20from%20KSEB%20only%20when%20the%20battery%20runs%20low%20or%20sunlight%20is%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20impressed%20me%20most%20is%20that%20the%20inverter%20draws%20daytime%20electricity%20directly%20from%20solar.%20Once%20the%20battery%20is%20charged%2C%20iCUBE%20shuts%20off%20the%20KSEB%20supply.%20If%20the%20sunlight%20is%20good%2C%20you%20can%20run%20600%E2%80%93700%20watts%20straight%20from%20solar.%20If%20the%20consumption%20exceeds%20that%2C%20it%20switches%20to%20KSEB%20seamlessly.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20the%20transition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Suresh%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Aliparamba%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20an%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20put%20the%20system%20to%20the%20test.%20A%20storm%20destroyed%2025%20electricity%20poles%20and%20blacked%20out%20his%20neighbourhood%20for%20five%20days.%20Yet%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20office%20remained%20powered.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20that%20entire%20week%2C%20I%20was%20practically%20off-grid.%20My%20work%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20even%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20street%20was%20dark.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20student%20idea%20that%20became%20a%20solar%20revolution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%E2%80%99s%20story%20reflects%20exactly%20what%20Harsh%20Mohan%20(34)%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20and%20his%20peers%20dreamt%20of%20back%20in%202011.%20Then%20undergraduates%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%2C%20Amritapuri%2C%20they%20were%20searching%20for%20a%20meaningful%20project%20when%20they%20stumbled%20upon%20something%20simple%20but%20striking%3A%20nearly%20every%20household%20in%20India%20had%20an%20inverter%2C%20but%20these%20machines%20consumed%20power%20daily%20just%20to%20stay%20alive%2C%20often%20adding%201.5%20to%20two%20units%20to%20the%20bill%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20solar%20was%20making%20headlines%2C%20but%20at%20a%20steep%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CInstalling%20rooftop%20solar%20meant%20discarding%20your%20existing%20inverter%20and%20buying%20a%20new%2C%20solar-compatible%20one.%20It%20was%20unaffordable%20for%20most%20families%20and%20created%20huge%20amounts%20of%20e-waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20challenge%20sparked%20an%20idea.%20Guided%20by%20his%20professor%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Harsh%20began%20tinkering%20with%20a%20solution%3A%20What%20if%2C%20instead%20of%20replacing%20inverters%2C%20they%20could%20create%20a%20small%20device%20that%20connected%20any%20inverter%20to%20solar%20panels%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20this%20idea%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20way%2C%20households%20could%20adopt%20solar%20without%20buying%20a%20new%20system%2C%20reducing%20both%20costs%20and%20pollution.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20solar%20accessible%20to%20middle-class%20families%2C%20not%20just%20the%20wealthy.%20Back%20then%2C%20panels%20were%20very%20expensive%2C%20and%20people%20thought%20solar%20was%20only%20for%20the%20rich.%20We%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20device%20became%20%E2%80%98iCON%E2%80%99%20(Intelligent%20Converter).%20%E2%80%9CSuddenly%2C%20families%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20spend%20lakhs%20on%20a%20new%20solar%20system.%20With%20a%20modest%20investment%20in%20iCON%20and%20panels%2C%20they%20could%20turn%20their%20old%20inverters%20into%20solar%20inverters%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20Left%3A%20Harsh%20Mohan%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gopal%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Kiran%20S.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495993%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20Left%3A%20Harsh%20Mohan%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gopal%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Kiran%20S.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20nearly%20five%20years%20of%20product%20iterations%20and%20patent%20work%2C%20Harsh%20and%20his%20colleagues%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20and%20Kiran%20S%2C%20formally%20launched%20%E2%80%98NyQuest%20Innovation%20Labs%20Pvt%20Ltd%E2%80%99.%20The%20company%20was%20later%20rebranded%20as%20Energy24by7%20to%20make%20the%20brand%20more%20customer-friendly%20and%20mission-driven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20feedback%20into%20a%20smarter%20inverter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20iCON%20opened%20doors%2C%20but%20customer%20feedback%20soon%20pushed%20the%20team%20further.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20told%20us%20their%20old%20inverters%20were%20noisy%2C%20inefficient%2C%20and%20bulky%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20new%20solar%20inverter%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20%E2%80%98iCUBE%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20high-efficiency%20smart%20solar%20UPS%20that%20brought%20together%20the%20roles%20of%20iCON%20and%20a%20regular%20inverter%20in%20one%20device.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20inverters%20in%20India%20run%20at%20a%20lower%20efficiency%2C%20but%20iCUBE%20tested%20at%20an%20impressive%20peak%20efficiency%20of%2097%20percent%E2%80%94making%20it%20even%20better%20than%20the%20benchmark%20five-star%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20efficiency%2C%20iCUBE%20was%20designed%20to%20adapt%20to%20household%20usage%20patterns%2C%20deciding%20when%20to%20use%20solar%2C%20when%20to%20draw%20from%20batteries%2C%20and%20when%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20grid.%20Their%20patented%20Battery%20Charging%20Inhibition%20(BCI)%20prevents%20wasteful%20charging%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20cutting%20hidden%20costs%20that%20many%20households%20never%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20the%20appeal%20is%20immediate%20for%20middle-income%20families.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20lowers%20bills%20by%20around%2040%E2%80%9350%20percent%20without%20massive%20upfront%20costs.%20The%20setup%20keeps%20homes%20running%20during%20outages%20for%20days.%20You%20can%20monitor%20its%20performance%20through%20our%20mobile%20app.%20It%20is%20compatible%20with%20lithium-ion%20and%20even%20EV%20batteries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Energy24by7%20has%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20across%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495990%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEnergy24by7%20has%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20across%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENavigating%20the%20challenges%20of%20building%20hardware%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20behind%20the%20success%20lay%20a%20long%20road%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20always%20been%20funding%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20co-founder%20Nishanth.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20hardware%20rarely%20gets%20the%20same%20attention%20as%20software.%20Investors%20like%20fast-scaling%20apps%20with%20quick%20returns.%20But%20hardware%20requires%20long-term%20investment%2C%20multiple%20prototypes%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishanth%20adds%20that%20every%20time%20they%20set%20up%20a%20system%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20they%20would%20discover%20something%20new%20the%20customer%20wanted.%20That%20meant%20going%20back%2C%20redesigning%2C%20and%20swapping%20out%20parts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20slow%2C%20painstaking%20process%20that%20most%20investors%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20patience%20for.%20What%20kept%20them%20going%20were%20the%20central%20and%20state%20government%20grants%20and%20support%20programmes%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20the%20runway%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Kerala%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Energy24by7%20has%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20across%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20is%20also%20making%20inroads%20into%20Africa%20with%20installations%20in%20Kenya%20and%20Zambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-3-1756908919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Energy24by7%20developed%20the%20iCUBE%2C%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20integrated%20solar%20UPS%20that%20ensures%20up%20to%2097%25%20energy%20efficiency.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-3-1756908919.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette