ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-19-at-5.54.41-PM_11zon-1756817017.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495393%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20learn%20and%20heal%20and%20grow%20when%20playing%20%E2%80%93%20so%20can%20the%20parents%3B%20Photo%20courtesy%20Swaati%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%20Prasad%2C%20seasoned%20special%20needs%20expert%20and%20current%20head%20of%20the%20Special%20Education%20Needs%20(SEN)%20Department%20at%20Step%20by%20Step%20School%20in%20Noida%2C%20recalls%20her%20first%20reaction%20to%20the%20term%20when%20she%20began%20her%20career%20in%20the%20late%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeeting%20me%20in%20her%20office%2C%20the%20picture%20of%20grace%20and%20calm%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSomeone%20told%20me%20about%20this%20new%20PG%20diploma%20teaching%20course%20that%E2%80%99s%20for%20special%20children.%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EYeh%20special%20kya%20hota%20hai%2C%20bachcha%20toh%20bachcha%20hota%20hai%20na%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E(What%20does%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%E2%80%9D%20mean%2C%20after%20all%3F%20A%20child%20is%20a%20child%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F)%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20instinctive%20response%20sets%20the%20tone%20for%20a%20key%20idea%20in%20this%20piece%3A%20understanding%20before%20labelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20neurodiversity%2C%20unlocking%20empathy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20to%20take%20away%20from%20the%20truth%20of%20neurodiversity%20%E2%80%94%20a%20term%20coined%20by%20Australian%20sociologist%20Judy%20Singer%20in%20her%201997%20undergraduate%20thesis%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20we%20are%20all%20wired%20differently.%20Rather%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20to%20understand%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20appreciate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20our%20individualities%20and%20identities%2C%20we%20first%20recognise%20the%20core%20truth%20of%20our%20similarities%20%E2%80%94%20unlocking%20empathy%20to%20activate%20compassion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hear%20my%20friend%20echo%20this%20thought%20when%20I%20ask%20her%20about%20the%20language%20around%20neurodiversity.%20Swaati%2C%20a%20classical%20dancer%20and%20writer%20navigating%20parenting%20and%20neurodivergence%20with%20her%2011-year-old%20son%20Aadi%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20harmonise%3B%20then%20we%20can%20get%20into%20specifics.%E2%80%9D%20She%20frames%20it%20within%20human%20evolution%2C%20drawing%20from%20%3Cem%3EAncestral%20Habits%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20social%20media%20handle%20that%20explores%20the%20relevance%20of%20ancestral%20practices%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDifferent%20kinds%20of%20people%20were%20needed%20to%20keep%20society%20going%20%E2%80%94%20those%20who%20can%20maintain%20order%20and%20those%20who%20are%20the%20thrill%20seekers.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20DNA%20evolved%20%E2%80%94%20for%20this%20strain%20that%20we%20now%20recognise%20as%20a%20defect%20only%20because%20modern%20life%20is%20all%20about%20these%20cookie-cutter%20moulds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-06-29-at-5.36.51-PM-2-1756816895-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Appreciating%20nature%20and%20taking%20quality%20time%20together%20is%20also%20parenting%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-06-29-at-5.36.51-PM-2-1756816895-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-06-29-at-5.36.51-PM-2-1756816895-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-06-29-at-5.36.51-PM-2-175681